      "content": "therapy and friends... they just don't get it. they think i'm just sad or going through a phase, but it's much more permanent than that. it's like i'm already gone. i'm just waiting for my body to realize it and catch up with what happened to my soul years ago. what do you do when you've already reached the end, but you're still stuck here?",
